short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_AU,en_GB,e: 批量下载物流轨迹和电子存根。
short.en: Download logistics tracks and electronic stubs in batches.
short.zh_TW: 批量下載物流軌跡和電子存根。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_AU,en_GB,e: LogisticsEnhancer 是一款用于获取物流信息的免费的浏览器扩展，其主要功能包括：批量截图物流轨迹、批量截图电子存根、一键导出物流轨迹信息、一键导出电子存根信息。
long.en: LogisticsEnhancer is a free browser extension for obtaining logistics information. Its main functions include: batch screenshots of logistics tracks, batch screenshots of electronic stubs, one-click export of logistics track information, and one-click export of electronic stub information.
long.zh_TW: LogisticsEnhancer 是一款用於獲取物流信息的免費的瀏覽器擴展，其主要功能包括：批量截圖物流軌跡、批量截圖電子存根、一鍵導出物流軌跡信息、一鍵導出電子存根信息。
